data.text:
Sardinia farmhouses: best agritourisms for your dream vacation in Italy

Book your farmhouse in Sardinia. Get ready to live at the best an ancient land, made up of flavors, traditions and cultures still incredibly alive.

From the North to the South, from the renowned Arzachena to Villasimius and the beaches around Cagliari, the Sardinian island is an amazing territory in its variety.

Explore the wildest areas of inland Sardinia, perhaps by booking a farm stay with swimming pool, so as not to miss anything.

But if you don't want to give up the coast, then find your accommodation in an agritourism near the sea, better during summer. Treat yourself with a lunch in a farmhouse to enjoy the rich Sardinian cuisine, with genuine and local products.

For those travelling with children, why not to choose a agriturismo with animals? The little ones will find the encounter with them undoubtedly interesting!
